project_descr: The overall purpose of the project ‘Regional Human Development Report on Multidimensional Progress’ in Barbados and the OECS is to improve human development assessment and promotion in the Caribbean through a number of avenues.

outputs.output_descr: In collaboration with the Regional  HDR Team, UNDP Barbados Country Office will seek to produce a micro narrative on multidimensional subjective well-being and lead the qualitative research that is being conducted for our respective territories.

project_title: human development report on multidimensional progress
